articles.title: Las Vegas Aces end Indiana Fever’s magical run in overtime Game 5 win to reach WNBA Finals - CNN
articles.description: The Las Vegas Aces survived a thriller Tuesday night to advance to the WNBA Finals for the fourth time in six years after a dramatic 107-98 overtime win against the Indiana Fever.
